---
title: Jerk Pork Chops with Thyme-Scented Rice and Beans and Sautéed Veggies
description: Tender pork coated in a tasty Jamaican-style jerk sauce is on the menu tonight! The sauce adds a bit of a kick to the dish, and the coconut milk adds a creaminess to the rice and beans... Yum!
